Class TorrentFile

java.lang.Object
org.torrent.bencoding.TorrentFile
public class TorrentFile
extends java.lang.Object
This class holds information related to the torrent file being downloaded

      private java.util.HashSet<ChannelData> channelDataStore
      A HashSet of all the channel data objects for each of the connections working on the target file. This is used to perform operations on every channel, such as adding messages to all of their queues.

      private TorrentFile.PieceSelectionPolicy piecePolicy

    • TorrentFile

      public TorrentFile​(java.nio.file.Path torrentFile, java.nio.file.Path targetLocation, TorrentFile.PieceSelectionPolicy pieceSelectionPolicy) throws java.io.IOException
      Constructor which parses a Bencoded .torrent file
      Parameters:
      torrentFile - The pathway to the .torrent file
      targetLocation - The intended output location of the file
      pieceSelectionPolicy - The policy to be used in choosing pieces for downloading
      Throws:
      java.io.IOException - If an error occurs in parsing the file or obtaining the tracker URL
